# prefix-block-open-at-eof

## Input

```
key {
```

## CST

```
SOURCE_FILE@0..5
  PREFIX_BLOCK@0..5
    WORD_KEY@0..3
      WORD@0..3 "key"
    SPACE@3..4 " "
    OPEN_BRACE@4..5 "{"
```

## Syntax Error

```
[
    SyntaxError {
        message: "missing closing '}' for prefix block",
        range: 5..5,
    },
]
```

## AST

```
SourceFile {
    shebang: none,
    items: [
        PrefixBlock {
            key: WordKey {
                word: WORD@0..3 "key",
            },
            open_brace: OPEN_BRACE@4..5 "{",
            items: [],
            close_brace: none,
        },
    ],
}
```

